# Gemini review raw dumps (provenance kept local; canonical record is the PLAN disposition tables)
.gemini-review-*.txt
/art-src/

# ── Internal working documents ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# This repo is PUBLIC (the -private suffix is historical). Internal material —
# dev plans, handoffs, audits, review packets — belongs in cli-pulse-internal,
# per the partner handover doc. These patterns keep a stray `git add -A` from
# publishing the untracked working set at the repo root permanently.
# Root-anchored so docs/ content is unaffected. Already-tracked files are
# unaffected by gitignore (e.g. historical DEV_PLAN/PROJECT_FIX commits stay).
/HANDOFF_*.md
/DEV_PLAN_*.md
/CODEX_*.md
/PROJECT_REVIEW*.md
/ART_ASSET_LIST*.md
/CLI_PULSE_ACTION_CHECKLIST*.md
